                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.34/12–747: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-12-08T11:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 8, 1947—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1483. In light Urtel 2346 December 7 Navy agreeable to release text of agreement
                    and exchange of notes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
